Package: twinfake
Title: Privacy-First Pipeline Twin Data for Code Development
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("twinfake contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "twinfake@example.invalid")
  )
Author: twinfake contributors
Maintainer: twinfake contributors <twinfake@example.invalid>
Description: Generates local, privacy-preserving dummy data sets that mirror
    schemas, file layouts, dirty data patterns, deterministic relationships, and
    join behaviour of sensitive analysis inputs. The generated data are intended
    for private code development and LLM-assisted pipeline construction, not for
    public release or as a substitute for formal disclosure-risk review.
